二、指定教科書及參考資料 Textbooks and Reference(請修課同學遵守智慧財產權，不得非法影印)


●指定教科書 Required TextsMicrosoft® 翻譯1 朱石炎著「刑事訴訟法 （上） 」。 2 林國賢、李春福合著「刑事訴訟法論」。
		●參考書資料暨網路資源 Reference Books and Online Resources最高法院刑事判例，最高法院刑事庭會議決議，最高法院刑事裁判。


三、教學目標 Objectives


期使學生瞭解刑事告訴、告訴之效力，檢察官之處理及檢察官不起訴處分之救濟方法，自訴之提出及其效力，將所學實體法及程序法之規定，適用於假設之個案，達到學以致用之目標。 


This course is to introduce and explore the procedure of filing criminal complaints, prosecutor’s investigation proceedings and measures, remedies for rulings not to prosecute, and filing private prosecutions as well as it’s consequence and result. The objective of this course is to enable students to apply statutes, criminal procedures and legal materials which they have learned to handle hypothetical cases and get some practical experience. By this way of learning, students can enrich their legal knowledge. 


